Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃·诺伊修凡·舒坦因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及  其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在正在西美翁大楼内展开着激战热斗…

Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于沉不住气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一帮蠢货们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站着等了好几个小时的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁都会忍耐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么奠基活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们666邀请过来  却是这个表现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个家伙  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会闯进我们这间屋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能摆平他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎还没得到新的肉体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会很快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗香  夏树  结爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  璃瑠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  本人原创的混合超必杀技  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特攻  熔岩-little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不稀罕你脱袜子的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以直接干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判决  死刑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了四天王之一的安路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  快治疗大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点来吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呸  抹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂上口水就Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治好就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重创到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  左天他醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我有些轻敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你干掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下你一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复意识了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  幸亏有迪斯克  夏娃  还有布雷德他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因为你自己很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  快瞧瞧看  在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被布雷德打了个七零八落  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像垃圾  破抹布一样惨兮兮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打倒了对方就损人家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此的话  至少把我最大的污点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给抹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩那么多力气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  她的目标是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  库鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趁机保护山田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个…什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你睡觉的功夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就痊愈了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安路卡的拳头怎么会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是血脉相连的姐弟  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的内心深处是有弱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  我没让拳头停住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是重力或是磁力的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不是…那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  退下吧  安路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚当·阿克莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂碎…我不再这么称呼你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让两位四天王败下阵来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要承认你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可算是出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里蹲的小少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许无礼  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是忘了  我是神这一事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷袭了我一下而已  别得意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  邀我们来这里而你自己却迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么害怕我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了  因为外面的人又吵了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让他们静下来可并不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过放心吧  我摆平一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆平了的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把外面的人们怎么样了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令璃瑠出动了少女部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女部队？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:33.63,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋する乙女には　常識通じない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:33.63,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱中的少女　完全不合情理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举办了一场少女部队的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家拍拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪一下子就安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真令人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想去看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人别这样  最终BOSS就在眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日所受的最大伤害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们换个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左天大人  请您走楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是四天王耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  去瞧瞧那些老头子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家来捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫结爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结爱酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后～我是穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗香酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在群众当中查出了数个NEEDLESS拥有未被我们图书馆记载的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璃瑠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我司西美翁大楼左翼顶层  瞭望台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这风景不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是旧东京
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们筑巢的爆炸中心地  Black Spot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是对你们而言的最后一道风景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没问过你的名字呢  神父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德  今天是值得纪念的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我获得新肉体的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个曾经属于布雷德的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态  凭什么想霸占我的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏那里有机器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不止是右眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个心脏和右眼的伤  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论动用多么高超的医疗技术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或是何种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没法治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一旦得到了你的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能进化为完美的神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像无数科学家们曾经描绘的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初见他的时候  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:13:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是有人拿亚当计划的遗产  造出了新的亚当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那个右眼和心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对错不了  他就是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男的有些眼熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六根道·银博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是左天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参与亚当计划的科学家之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚当计划  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说那次爆炸的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你之外还有别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初我也不相信自己的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向城里的科学家们卖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把自己变成神的克隆体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人渣  立即给我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雨细丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dean·Drive-F·H  +
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高温爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一次都打不着他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吞噬了迄今为止见过的所有NEEDLESS  或让他们沦为仆下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的能力都集聚于我一身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  你此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在与我认识的所有NEEDLESS为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…迄今为止都那么努力地闯关斩将杀到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把虚伪的勇气挂在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什么「努力终有回报」  「可能性不为零」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些自作多情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是弱者的自我暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力和祈祷  影响不了奇迹的发生率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只蚂蚁吵吵嚷嚷的  改变不了星球的运行轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球甚至不知道蚂蚁它存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力和祈祷  影响不了奇迹发生的发生率  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什么「怒了就能胜利」  「同伴死了就要赢」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些漂亮的奇迹根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对我来说  根本没有依赖奇迹的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然与以往的敌人不可同日而语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  缺少本该拥有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来告诉你好了  ZERO的真正能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么巨大的little boy啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我这个原型的还要大好多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么他的招数会增强威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是  积极反馈·ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积极反馈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积极反馈就是  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以核裂变为代表的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种反应被增幅促进  形成连锁反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难理解啊  脑袋快要喷火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经喷火咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的简单一些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是从互相吵架上升为打架斗殴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么阿克莱特的积极反馈·ZERO是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  把所受的招数加强数倍再返给对方的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积极反馈这个能力  最终会趋向于大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是最强的能力  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷德的能力  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把所受的招数原模原样返给对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿克莱特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却能把任何攻击加强之后再返给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够始终使用比对手厉害的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比它还强的能力  可以说是不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回旋引力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向天吐痰  就会返回给自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回旋引力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…不可能有胜算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与天作对  要悉数返还给自身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四波动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是单方蹂躏啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克莱特这家伙  又强了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是阿克莱特毫发无损地活下来  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的安排可就乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个神父没那么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能看到曙光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体验绝望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是失败作与神的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然避开了我的要害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没察觉到吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么自愿让你戳穿我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于有机会钻进你的怀里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我夺来吧  把你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用额头的白毫把阿克莱特的能力全都夺过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  才不是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克莱特不敢三两下就杀死布雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  阿克莱特的目的是霸占神父的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而心脏附近正是他最想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能扎穿心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引力子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好方法  一起封住了自己和阿克莱特的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不妨就打飞你脖子上面的部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引力子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  被抵消了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间在扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋里有影像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不是  逆排斥反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆排斥反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  和那时一样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  那段令人忌恨的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恢复…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶啊  瑟肯多莉娅那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「左天大人  请您走楼梯」  啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说那部烂电梯  才能装得下这点人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会有谁偷偷带着很重的东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如金属块什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的胳膊就是